{"tid":691997,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook承認與華為等中國科技公司分享數據","createTime":"2018-06-06T08:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T04:11:29.000Z","uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"56b14fdc9368c03eca1127331b61aabbd929cc97","tid":691997,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"《紐約時報》報道，Facebook與至少四家中國科技公司有數據共享協議，而該協議可追溯至2010年。根據協議內容，Facebook允許華為、聯想、廣東歐珀移動通信和TCL集團訪問設備用戶及其朋友的詳細信息。但Facebook表示，可能於本周結束與華為的協議。<br />\n<br />\n美國情報機構警告，華為與中國政府關係密切，可能對國家安全構成威脅，惟Facebook指，Facebook的用戶數據並沒有儲存在華為的服務器上。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，Facebook與逾60家公司有數據共享協議，當中包括蘋果公司和亞馬遜公司。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook用戶私隱問題已惹來市場關注。蘋果早前在全球開發大會(WWDC)上宣布，之後推出新iOS和Mac作業系統版本時，會嘗試阻截Facebook自動追蹤網絡用戶的工具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1528251993476&amp;issue=20180606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1528251993476%26issue%3D20180606&d=TTCSStd0SLCqKvy40WHKmgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=b76cf460\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1528251993476%26issue%3D20180606&h=efef9e78\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1528251993476&amp;issue=20180606</a>"},{"pid":"e0976aab24aac954a41bf73e0289b9b0d472cf55","tid":691997,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"Molamola 資料上政府server<br />\n你第日出唔到境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349367f054eaab3be2c36898857f95839bcecaad","tid":691997,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"支那機，預咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc1ce5846e86397cdac47f5756eda0b3bfc1506","tid":691997,"uid